The problem: I can&#39;t exactly put my finger on it, but this deck sucks royal ass. I haven&#39;t won yet. I blame this on not being a weave player, but I&#39;m sure other things are to blame, such as my lack of deckbuilding skills. At any rate, this deck isn&#39;t really here for you to ogle over it&#39;s sheer power, I need some bloody help....How can I make this a viable deck based around the lascinth strategy? </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
